#: ../../../variable/CTEST_PRESETS_FILE.rst:2
msgid "CTEST_PRESETS_FILE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CTEST_PRESETS_FILE.rst:6
msgid ""
"Specify the ``PRESETS_FILE`` option for all relevant :manual:`ctest(1)` :ref:"
"`Dashboard Client` step commands in a dashboard script, or on the :program:"
"`ctest` command line via the :ctest-dashboard-option:`-D` option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CTEST_PRESETS_FILE.rst:10
msgid ""
"This variable sets the ``PRESETS_FILE`` option for :command:"
"`ctest_configure`, :command:`ctest_build`, :command:`ctest_test`, and :"
"command:`ctest_memcheck` when those commands are not given an explicit "
"``PRESETS_FILE`` argument."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../variable/CTEST_PRESETS_FILE.rst:15
msgid ""
"See also :variable:`CTEST_PRESET`, :variable:`CTEST_CONFIGURE_PRESET`, :"
"variable:`CTEST_BUILD_PRESET`, and :variable:`CTEST_TEST_PRESET`."
msgstr ""
